text:
Yuika always keeps an eye out for everyone.
Thank you, as always.

No, no, no.
Sakuyan is always working for everyone's sake too...!
Hey, Producer, you think so too, right?

You both have
a lot of initiative.

Both of you
care about your friends.

The other day, you made dried flowers, right?
Kiriko was really happy about that.

! That's good—
I'm happiest when everyone else is happy.

That's right, isn't it!
Sakuyan always helps out when someone's in trouble—

Hehe, it's mutual, isn't it?
As important comrades, we need to support each other, right?

Oh, thanks, Producer.
But if we're talking about lightening the mood, Yuika is better at it—

Hey, are you coming back to Yuika!?
For Yuika, having Sakuyan around is essential—
